Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss that elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My! It's coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,this is a real elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real baby elephant. I'm going to make it my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's prohibited to capture real animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare to stop me, stupid robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it came from some hunting prohibited area nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a safari park made only with robots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his fault for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I hunt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Atom. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a robot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Little Elephant Pura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is quite big for a robot safari park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! A real elephant has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then go over to that side. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an invisible beam fence around this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where did this elephant come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can never enter this place! It must be a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is a real...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave. I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a real one for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is true that it did come from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's late. Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu. Welcome to our safari park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor Hura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Isn't this a wonderful park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel reluctant to use animals for hunting even if they were robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Real animals are decreasing in its number recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I developed animal robots that's the same as real ones
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so tourists can observe them and enjoy hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I opened this safari park in this vast field of Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the improved version of flamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insert money here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-How is it? Do you want a glass? -I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of three lions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I caught a leopard and two hippos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you need for safari,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,from guns to clothes, you can borrow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are different classes; Class A gets a jeep and two assistant robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Class B only gets a jeep, and Class C gets one assistant robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just beyond my imagination. Thank you for inviting, but I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I called you because I wanted to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He thinks I'm his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a robot as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come out now. It's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, bad snakes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you alone since it's so dangerous around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We robots are also friends with animals, as well as with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Since it's hard to call you, I'm going to name you Pura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura. How is it? Isn't it a good name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you guide me to where you first entered this park?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be tough if another animals enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a place for repairing hunted robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, Doctor Ochanomizu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,please take a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very aggressive elephant called Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very aggressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All animal robots here are designed not to take people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this Zora is different. It kills people ruthlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you build such dangerous thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be any thrill if there weren't a crazy beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one is too dangerous. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rebuild this Zora to listen to what workers here say at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm going to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Doctor Ochanomizu. Visitors are also expecting a lot from Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure leaves me some profit as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not right. You are doing this for the sake of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I became a scientist to earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A man like you is not suitable for the world of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hura, a real elephant is shot dead near the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There are real animals outside this park, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there must be some place where they enter through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's impossible! -How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the surveillance panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can detect even a little bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did the elephant enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will investigate it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Later isn't enough. Another similar accident will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, you should hurry and finish rebuilding Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hura, so you don't mind getting wild animals killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't invent animal robots,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,more wild animals would have been killed by humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Zora moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My gosh. I can't do anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond curbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom is the only one who can take care of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura, not ready yet? It's evening already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Doctor Ochanomizu to worry, so I'm going to go tell him what happened and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So please wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll soon be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You are late, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry? So Doctor Ochanomizu already went out with Doctor Hura to find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would Doctor Ochanomizu be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that robot take the baby elephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he hasn't given up on Pura yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that robot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura, it's your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. You are safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go find Doctor Ochanomizu now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel alone? I'm here next to you. Relax and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. You are such a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spend the night with Pura tonight. Please do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's pretty cold during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Doctor Hura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it seems like we got into trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Hura, what in the world has happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are cannibals doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are also the robots I built.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then stop them! -Well that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They will let you go if you pay $100.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much. Making money even with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pay extra $500, they will make you their chief. How does that sound like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, where in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going? Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Zora, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a suction power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get rid of it if Pura weren't with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not your mom, Pura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow it immediately. Don't lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Pura. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go check it, so you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a passage in this kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura and his mom must have entered through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything suspicious. If you do, the baby elephant won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, right? What's behind that waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not going to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a passage leading to where wild animals are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? Real animals? -Is that for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guide us to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, surely they are not going to cut our heads off for real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They will just pretend to do it, unless they have some kind of breakdowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakdowns? My, that's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I made you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help. My blood is draining to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You will fall if you keep wriggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello. Control Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zora has escaped the surveillance and has invaded the wild animal protection area!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, don't do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'm going to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Look at that. -Oh, that's a legion of elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to enjoy a real safari after not having one for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you guys really going to shoot real elephants?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a passage behind the waterfall. We can just say that we thought this place was also a part of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Don't cut in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place for perfect aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zora. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zora! I'm going to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Pura. Now it's time to say goodbye. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be happiest when you are with your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea there was this kind of natural passage behind the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have investigated it more thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know about this passage, but Pura's mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's beyond recovery now because of Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all good now, Doctor Hura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right! Let's build an ocean safari next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a great item!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannibal whale this time? Don't invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Where are you? Let's go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pura, you really are doing your best to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Pura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bee Island is full of all kinds of flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran! You will go missing if you run around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd things keep happening on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a huge underground city in that creepy cave there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Swarm of honeybees ruling over people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Bee, you are here now. Let me deal with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Secret of Bee Island." Please look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Secret of Bee Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
